	(8, 9, '975072A6', 'Michelle Ann', 'Espisua', '1988-07-05', '', '', 'mishyes05@gmail.com', '+639172471752', '3 Main Drive, Mintcor Southrow Townhouse, Brgy. Cupang, West Service Rd, Alabang, Muntinlupa City ', 'Lot 22, Block 41-D, Phase 4D, Heritage Homes, Loma De Gato, Marilao, Bulaca', '', 'Manila', '1771', 'I recently read about the job posting for Sales &amp; Operations Planners &amp; Managers (S&amp;OP). I would like to introduce myself to you as I believe I have the skills, qualifications and experience necessary to make a significant contribution to your organization.\r\n\r\nI&#039;m grateful of finishing my Master&#039;s Degree in Business Administration and achieving early my Managerial Position. I work directly for the top management for almost 10 years now most of them are CEO&#039;s or owner of the company. I learned how to coordinate and to have a better corporate/business mindset because of these mentors on how to help them grow their company as they believe on my skills. Supporting and helping the top management to be organized, brain storming with different strategies to make the company more securely competitive and motivating staffs while achieving company&#039;s mission vision is my favorite part of my job because of the chance of improving myself and learning with others at the same time. Managing from administrative to production of staffs and company&#039;s overall operation of improving process procedure, monitoring, reporting, documentation and coordination is my forte.\r\n\r\nMy goal now is to achieve having an online job at home and still have a balance life for myself. I would still love to share my knowledge and potential to a company/someone that would believe and interested to hire me here.', 'Management, Operations, Productions, Warehousing, SOPs and Multi-Tasking', '1532084957.pdf', '30 mbps', '1532084957.pdf', NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0'),
	(9, 6, 'BB624811', 'Lovely Ann', 'Ilan', '1984-09-25', '', '', 'lovely_ilan@yahoo.com', '9174207168', 'B9 L6 St. Mary Village', 'Santa Rosa', '', 'Laguna', '4026', 'Hi, \r\n\r\nMy heart skip when I read job Onlinejob.net for a Order Processor. I decided to apply immediately. Data-driven and highly analytical, I bring to the table 5 years of experience as a business analyst able to influence corporate growth strategies through fact-based, data-driven insights and analysis.\r\n\r\nI have worked as a business analyst for manufacturing company, currently working as Senior Demand Planner and has a part time job as Reporting Specialist and Data Analysis . In each position, I planned and directed analysis of complex initiatives ranging from proposed mergers, acquisitions and divestitures to Kaizen based process improvements, organizational restructures and product launch proposals.\r\n\r\nAreas of success include:\r\n\r\nExpert in Data Visualization and Data Mining\r\n\r\nProducing detailed analytics and actionable reports that show key performance indicators, identify areas of improvement and facilitate informed decision making.\r\n\r\nMinimizing uncertainty, removing ambiguity and synthesizing large amounts of complex data into clear, concise and meaningful contexts.\r\n\r\nLeading system and process reengineering to capture improved efficiencies, fail-safe business continuity and multimillion-dollar cost savings.\r\n\r\nConducting in-depth data mining, visualization and analysis to uncover and rectify process weaknesses and vulnerabilities, mitigate risk and resolve business and QV developer\r\n\r\nAs you can see, I am committed to being a positive driver of company goals and confident in my ability to improve operational performance. I am available to interview anytime and look forward to speaking with you. You can call me at (63) 09174207168 or email me lovely_ilan@yahoo.com.\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n\r\nLovely Ann Ilan\r\n', 'Order management, reporting, data analysis, data visualization, ', '1532360984.pdf', 'https://www.bandwidthplace.com/results/5b55f7536e6b48.78836904-72687651/?source=copy', '1532360984.JPG', NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0'),
	(10, 4, '22F45734', 'SomayahrA', 'Radiamoda', '1992-01-08', '', '', 'mayahradiamoda@yahoo.com', '+639359278973', 'Lot 8 Blk 8 NHA Bangkal Davao City', '', '', 'Philippines', '8000', 'Dear Sir/Maâ€™am,\r\n\r\n\r\n              I graduated with a bachelorâ€™s degree in finance from Ateneo de Davao University and I am interested in any vacant position that is related to my course. The nature of my degree course has prepared me for any position. It involved a great deal of independent research, requiring initiative, self-motivation and a wide range of skills. I can take on the responsibility of any position, and determination to ensure that I make a success of it. \r\n\r\nI am a conscientious person who works hard and pays attention to detail. I am confident that my skills and past experience could make great contributions to your organization. My current objective is to obtain a position that will fully utilize my skills and offer an opportunity for continued professional growth. I believe I could fit easily into your team. I&#039;m flexible, quick to pick up new skills and eager to learn from others. I also have lots of ideas and enthusiasm.\r\n\r\n\r\nI am positive that my skills and knowledge gives more weight to my application over others. I look forward to a future discussion where I can demonstrate my passion in becoming an integral member of your company.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThank you for taking out the time to read this.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSincerely, \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSomayah Radiamoda\r\nApplicant', 'Multi-tasking,Ability to make decisions and solve problems,Ability to obtain and process information,Ability to plan, organize and prioritize work,Ability to analyze quantitative data,Quick to learn with good interpersonal and organizational skills,Have a high sense of responsibility.', '1532372530.docx', 'https://www.bandwidthplace.com/results/5b562489e8c414.97798158-72692068/?source=copy', '', NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0'),
